Rock Solid Industries

RSI Tradesman Rack

Amarok

Dimensions: 1700mm  x 1260mm x 90 mm

Ranger / Hilux / D-Max / Bt-50

Dimensions: 1700mm  x 1156mm x 90 mm

USA Trucks

Dimensions: 1900mm  x 1356mm x 90 mm

  • Black epoxy powder-coated T6 aluminium
  • Approximate Installed Weight 25kg
  • T Slot Extrusions
  • Universally Compatible with M8 Bolts.

 

Click here to view the entire range of RSI SmartCap Evo Canopies available!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!

 

Please note: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for the RSI Tradesman Rack product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
